ts of sea-level rise and increasing storminess become more apparent. Within the last decade there has been a realisation that an important way to protect the coastline in a sustainable manner is for all parties with a stake in the coastal and marine environment to coordinate their activities within an ongoing economic, management and legislative framework. This Integrated Coastal Zone Management is being actively adopted within this region, and is likely to be the key to the long-term protection of the English Channel.},
author = {Holligan, PM and Harris, RP and Newell, RC and Harbour, DS and Head, RN and Linley, EAS and Lucas, MI and Tranter, PRG and Weekley, CM},
doi = {10.3354/meps014111},
